steps.name: And I click the hyperlink named "Row1Row1Tile2Icon002"
And I move to the next attribute
** Jurnale
* Purchase documents/Documente de achizi
And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu002Row1UIGroup00004Row1Row1Tile1Title136"
Then "Purchase documents" window is opened
And I close "Purchase documents" window

And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu002Row1UIGroup00004Row2Row2Tile1Title026"
Then "Accounting documents" window is opened
And I close "Accounting documents" window

And I click the hyperlink named "Submenu002Row1UIGroup00001Row1Row1Tile1Title022"
Then "Purchase Invoices" window is opened
And I click the button named "FormCreate"
Then "Purchase Invoice (create)" window is opened
And I close "Purchase Invoice (create)" window
Then "Purchase Invoices" window is opened
And I close "Purchase Invoices" window

And I close "Notice of entry (create)" window

And I close "Notice of entries" window

And I close "Customs declaration (create)" window
